The paper discusses the role of artificial intelligence in decision-making and its potential impact on human subjectivity and free will. This topic is closely related to the field of AI (cs.AI), as well as the sub-categories of cybernetics (cs.CY), ethics in technology (cs.ET), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
